OL,3,CDefibrillators and bleed control kits
OL,4,Cto be installed in Nationwide branches
OL,6,FNationwide Building Society is
OL,7,Finstalling defibrillators and bleed
OL,8,Fcontrol kits across its 605 branches.
OL,10,FThe rollout, which will see the kits
OL,11,Finstalled from now until the end of
OL,12,Fthe year, is in partnership with Visa.
OL,14,FSt John Ambulance is also working
OL,15,Falongside Nationwide to offer life-
OL,16,Fsaving training to 4,000 members of
OL,17,Fstaff as well as local communities.
OL,19,FNationwide has previously promised to
OL,20,Fkeep all branches open until at least
OL,21,F2030.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
