OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780625006
OL,3,CDefibrillators and bleed control kits
OL,4,Cto be installed in Nationwide branches
OL,6,FAmanda Beech, Nationwide's director of
OL,7,Fretail services, said: "By
OL,8,Ftransforming our branches into
OL,9,Fvisible, emergency hubs, we're making
OL,10,Fit easier to access help when every
OL,11,Fsecond counts.
OL,13,F"Crucially we're also offering
OL,14,Ftraining to all our branch colleagues,
OL,15,Fbefore extending that training into
OL,16,Fthe communities we serve.
OL,18,F"We want more people to feel prepared,
OL,19,Fconfident and ready to act when it
OL,20,Fmatters most."
OL,26,@oD@XOUuD@AOUzD@AOU|D@NO]
