OL,3,CDefibrillators and bleed control kits
OL,4,Cto be installed in Nationwide branches
OL,6,FSt John Ambulance chief medical
OL,7,Fofficer Professor Andrew Hartle said:
OL,8,F"We're so pleased to work with
OL,9,FNationwide and Visa on this project,
OL,10,Fwhich so perfectly meets St John
OL,11,FAmbulance's mission to put the power
OL,12,Fof first aid into everyone's hands.
OL,14,F"With hundreds more public access
OL,15,Fdefibrillators and bleed control kits
OL,16,Facross the UK, and thousands more
OL,17,Fpeople confident to use them, I am
OL,18,Fconfident many more lives will be
OL,19,Fsaved in our communities."
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU{D@ZO]
